trans-unit.source: Provides a base class for a Web server control <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" />.
trans-unit.target: Udostępnia klasę podstawową dla kontrolki serwera sieci Web <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" />.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem> provides a base class for toolbox items that create Web server controls.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem> udostępnia klasę podstawową dla elementów przybornika tworzenia kontrolki serwera sieci Web.

trans-unit.source: This class extends <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> and provides the following additional methods:
trans-unit.target: Ta klasa rozszerza <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> i udostępnia następujące metody dodatkowe:

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolAttributeValue%2A> gets the value of an attribute of the toolbox item.
<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolHtml%2A> gets the HTML that represents the initial state of the control.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolHtml%2A> pobiera kod HTML, który reprezentuje początkowy stan formantu.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolType%2A> gets the type of the associated runtime component.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.GetToolType%2A> pobiera typ składnika skojarzone środowiska wykonawczego.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem" /> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem" /> class.
The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.DisplayName%2A> is set to a short version of the type name.
The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of the tool for this toolbox item.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Type" /> Narzędzia dla tego elementu przybornika.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem" /> class using the provided type.
trans-unit.target: Tworzy nowe wystąpienie klasy <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem" /> przy użyciu podanego typu.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem.DisplayName%2A> is set to a short version of the type name.
A SerializationInfo object containing information needed to instantiate the Web control through deserialization.
trans-unit.target: Obiektu SerializationInfo, zawierający informacje potrzebne do formantu sieci Web do deserializacji.

trans-unit.source: A StreamingContext object.

Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem" /> class using the provided <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> object and <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" />.
trans-unit.target: Tworzy nowe wystąpienie klasy <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem" /> przy użyciu dostarczonego <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> obiektu i <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost" /> for the current design document.
Creates objects from each type contained in this <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" />, and adds them to the specified designer.
trans-unit.target: Tworzy obiekty z każdego typu zawartych w tym <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" />i dodaje je do określonego projektanta.

trans-unit.source: An array of created <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IComponent" /> objects.

<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A> always throws an exception, indicating that the method is inherited from <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> and only intended for use with Windows Forms.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A> zawsze zgłasza wyjątek, wskazujący, że metoda jest odziedziczone <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> i jest przeznaczona tylko do użytku z formularzy systemu Windows.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore(System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost)" /> method is only available in Windows Forms.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore(System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost)" /> Metoda jest dostępna tylko w formularzach systemu Windows.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> that describes the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem" />.
A <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" /> that indicates the serialization stream characteristics.
Loads the state of the toolbox item from the specified serialization information object.
trans-unit.target: Ładuje stan elementu przybornika z serializacji określonego obiektu informacji.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost" /> for the current design document.
The type of attribute to retrieve the value of.
Gets the value of the specified type of attribute of the toolbox item.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera wartość określonego typu atrybutu element przybornika.

trans-unit.source: The value of the specified type of attribute.
The default implementation will throw an <xref:System.ArgumentException> if the `attributeType` parameter is anything other than a <xref:System.Web.UI.PersistChildrenAttribute>.
trans-unit.target: Domyślna implementacja zgłosi <xref:System.ArgumentException> Jeśli `attributeType` parametr jest cokolwiek innego niż <xref:System.Web.UI.PersistChildrenAttribute>.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="attributeType" /> parameter is not a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.PersistChildrenAttribute" />.
The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost" /> for the current design document.
Gets the HTML for the Web control that the tool creates.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera kod HTML dla formantu sieci Web narzędzie tworzy.

trans-unit.source: The HTML for the Web control that the tool creates.
trans-unit.target: Kod HTML dla formantu sieci Web narzędzie tworzy.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost" /> for the current design document.
Gets the type of this toolbox item.
The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of this toolbox item.
The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of the Web server control toolbox item.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Type" /> Elementu przybornika kontrolki serwera sieci Web.

trans-unit.source: Initializes this toolbox item.
The <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo" /> used to save the state of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControlToolboxItem" />.
A <see cref="T:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext" /> that indicates the serialization stream characteristics.
Saves the state of the toolbox item to the specified serialization information object.
trans-unit.target: Zapisuje stan elementu przybornika do serializacji określonego obiektu informacji.
